<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@200&display=swap');
    </style>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8" http-equiv="Content-Type">
  <title>Welcome to Onboarder</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@200&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@200&display=swap');
    body {
      -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
      -webkit-text-size-adjust:none;
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif !important;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #151515;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .body {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      color: #151515;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      background: var(--Background-color, #FFFBF5);
    }

    h1, p{
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--Black, #151515);
      background: var(--white-active, #FFF);
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .welcome-heading {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .image {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .button {
        text-align: center;
    }
    .content-text {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      color: #000;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .login-details {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .login-details p {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .sign-in-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 18px 30px;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--Black, #151515);
      background: var(--Chart-purple, #9923AC);
      box-shadow: 1px 1px 0px 0px #000;
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none !important;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    a, span {
        text-decoration: none !important;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .contact-info {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #000;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .support-email {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      color: #9923AC !important;
      text-decoration: underline !important;
    }
    .footer {
      font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #888;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="body">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="welcome-heading" style="font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif">Welcome to Onboarder</h1>
    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/HL1KrkjH/email.jpg" alt="Onboarder Image">
    </div>
    <p class="content-text" style="font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif">
      We are so glad that you have joined us and we hope that you will enjoy using our features and services.
      To help you get started, we have created an account for you with the following login details:
    </p>

    <div class="login-details" style="font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif">
        <p>Email: <span>{{email}}</span></p>
        <p>Password: <span>{{password}}</span></p>
      <p>You can use these login details to access your account from any browser.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="button" style="font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif">
        <a href="https://onboarder-untitled.netlify.app/employee/signin" class="sign-in-button">Sign In</a>
    </div>

    <p class="content-text" style="font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif">
      If you have any questions or feedback, please feel free to contact us at
      <span class="support-email">support@onboarder.com</span>.
      We are always happy to hear from you and assist you in any way we can.
    </p>

    <p class="content-text" style="font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif">
      Thank you for choosing our app, and we look forward to seeing you soon. ðŸ˜Š
    </p>
    <div class="footer" style="font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif">
        &copy; 2023 Onboarder. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
